snippet.title: Hatsune Miku Jigsaw Puzzle
snippet.description:
Multiplayer jigsaw puzzle has been released!
You can play on your own, or share controllers with your friend and play up to 2 players co-op!

39 illustrations are available!
Choose your favorite illustration and play the jigsaw puzzle!

■Title: Hatsune Miku Jigsaw Puzzle
■Release date: March 24th, 2022 (Thursday)
■Genre: Puzzle
■Supported hardware: Nintendo Switch
■Number of players: 1-2
■Suggested retail price: 1,500 yen
■Purchasing method: Nintendo eShop (download-only software)
■Twitter：https://twitter.com/cfm_mobile

#HatsuneMiku
